Job Description:
 Incrementar el Nivel de facturación de acuerdo a las metas Señaladas; 
- Detectar potenciales Clientes y/o Oportunidades de negocio; 
- Brindar capacitaciónes tanto Internas como Externas; 
- Dar soporte especializado al resto del equipo de Ventas; 
- Promover nuestro conocimiento, experiencia, capacidad y confianza en brindar soluciones relacionadas al producto y/o sistemas. Incluye la promoción del beneficio que la técnica y las características especiales que el producto pueda dar; 
- Detectar la demanda de los productos; 
- Proponer nuevos productos para ampliar el portafolio de la empresa; 
- Responsable de la gestión de Ventas en clientes especialmente asignados.

As a Field Service Engineer You will be an expert in rotating equipment, focused on site activities management such as planning, manpower resources/tools assignment and technical assistance to complete the work scope according to the contractual requirements.
As a specialist in control field service engineering you will:
 Supervise the installation, calibration and set up of instruments;
 Supervise cable laying, meggering and connection;
 Lead and execute loop check and commissioning phase, performing the functional tests;
 Lead and execute unit start-up and performance tests;
 Perform and coordinate software and PLC troubleshooting including network communication with external devices in the plant;
 Perform software upgrade and correction implementation on PLCs and all additional Network devices;
 Update and submit documentation as-builts and software implementations;
 Work with ToolBox ST; Mark VIe controller; HImatrix, BN 3500 panel configuration;
 Perform and supervise BN sensors installation, configuration, and calibration;
 Perform and supervise equipment startup; know the LM2500+ & PGT 25 operation; know Compressor operation (including Antisurge logic)
